@devinbost Were you able to run the test provided by @sijie to confirm that it works?

I think the create topic command below, fails because the tenant and namespace weren't created first. 
`$ bin/pulsar-admin topics create persistent://example-tenant/ingest/example-kafka-topic`

regarding uploading schema, I have the steps as the followings for your reference:

```
$ cat schema.json
{
    "type": "STRING",
    "schema": "",
    "properties": {}
}
$ bin/pulsar-admin schemas upload -f schema.json test-string-schema
$ bin/pulsar-admin schemas get test-string-schema
{
  "name": "test-string-schema",
  "schema": "",
  "type": "STRING",
  "properties": {}
}
```

